UID:987724
DESCRIPTION:<p>Six spellers enter\, but only one can win <em>The 25th Annu
 al Putnam County Spelling Bee</em>! <br /><br />As six wonderfully unique 
 and impassioned contestants vie for the championship by spelling their way
  through vexing vocabulary\, hilarious and poignant personal stories unfol
 d&hellip\;along with a dash of riotous audience participation.<br /><br />
 This charmingly witty and touching musical has entertained audiences acros
 s the world since its Tony&ndash\;winning Broadway debut in 2005. It now r
 eturns to New York in a special 20th Anniversary production that celebrate
 s the singular heart\, humor\, and verve that cemented its place in the mu
 sical theater canon. Featuring a Tony Award-winning book by Rachel Sheinki
 n (Striking 12\, <em>Sleeping Beauty Wakes</em>) and a vibrant score by To
 ny Award winner William Finn (<em>Falsettos</em>\, A New Brain)\, <em>The 
 25th Annual Putnam County Spelling Bee</em> is a fast-paced and funny D-E-
 L-I-G-H-T.</p>
